---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="My AI-Powered Web Development Stack (2026): Tools, Workflow, and Setup"
  description="A comprehensive guide to the AI tools and workflow powering modern web development in 2026. Discover the stack behind Shelby Web Company."
>
  <article class="pt-32 pb-24 px-4 bg-[#0A0A0A]">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Header -->
      <header class="mb-16 text-center">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 mb-6 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-brand-cyan/20 bg-brand-cyan/5">
          <span class="text-brand-cyan text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Digital Strategy</span>
          <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-brand-cyan/30"></span>
          <span class="text-brand-sky/60 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-widest">Vol #1 Article #6 • April 2026</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="font-heading text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-white mb-8 tracking-tight leading-[1.1]">
          My AI-Powered <br />
          <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-cyan to-brand-blue">Web Development Stack (2026)</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-brand-sky/80 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          If you're looking for the best AI tools for web development in 2026, the answer isn't a single tool—it's a stack.
        </p>
      </header>

      <!-- Main Image Placeholder -->
      <div class="aspect-video bg-brand-dark border border-white/5 rounded-3xl mb-16 overflow-hidden shadow-2xl relative group">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-blue/20 to-transparent opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
           <span class="text-brand-sky/20 font-heading text-4xl font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] transform -rotate-12 text-center px-4">Shelby Web Company <br/> Tech Stack 2026</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-lg text-brand-sky/90 mb-12">
          Over the past year, <a href="/" class="text-brand-cyan hover:underline decoration-brand-cyan/30 underline-offset-4">Shelby Web Company</a> has refined a workflow that combines multiple AI tools to speed up development, improve code quality, and reduce friction between idea and execution.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="text-brand-accent">01.</span> What Is an AI-Powered Development Stack?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-brand-sky/80 mb-8">Instead of relying on one platform alone, you create a unique system where each tool does what it's best at. This approach gives you:</p>
        
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16">
          <div class="bg-brand-dark/50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 text-center">
            <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-2">Better Performance</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/60 text-sm">Optimized tools for specific tasks</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-dark/50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 text-center">
            <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-2">More Flexibility</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/60 text-sm">Switch between tools as needed</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-dark/50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 text-center">
            <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-2">Faster Iteration</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/60 text-sm">Quick prototyping and testing</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="text-brand-accent">02.</span> The Core Tools
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-8 mb-16">
          <div class="bg-brand-dark border border-white/5 p-8 rounded-3xl">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Code Editors</h3>
            <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div>
                <strong class="text-brand-cyan block mb-2">Visual Studio Code</strong>
                <p class="text-brand-sky/70 text-sm">Best for stability, massive extension ecosystem, and full environmental control.</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-brand-cyan block mb-2">Windsurf</strong>
                <p class="text-brand-sky/70 text-sm">Designed for AI collaboration and rapid prototyping with an AI-native interface.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-brand-dark border border-white/5 p-8 rounded-3xl">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Coding Assistants</h3>
            <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div>
                <strong class="text-brand-cyan block mb-2">Claude Code</strong>
                <p class="text-brand-sky/70 text-sm">Incredibly strong for complex logic, deep reasoning, and refactoring large codebases.</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-brand-cyan block mb-2">OpenCode</strong>
                <p class="text-brand-sky/70 text-sm">Lightweight and fast-moving. Ideal for generating boilerplate and quick iterations.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-brand-dark border border-white/5 p-8 rounded-3xl">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Infrastructure & Prototyping</h3>
            <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div>
                <strong class="text-brand-cyan block mb-2">OpenRouter & Ollama</strong>
                <p class="text-brand-sky/70 text-sm">Flexibility to switch between cloud models and running models locally for privacy and offline speed.</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-brand-cyan block mb-2">Lovable & Vercel</strong>
                <p class="text-brand-sky/70 text-sm">Fast MVP building and instant deployment for modern web frameworks.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-brand-blue/5 border-l-4 border-brand-blue p-8 my-12 rounded-r-2xl">
          <p class="text-white font-medium italic mb-0">"AI isn't replacing developers—it's amplifying them. The real shift is in faster iteration, more experimentation, and better tooling."</p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="text-brand-accent">03.</span> The 2026 Workflow
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 mb-16">
          {[
            "Start with an idea in Lovable for rapid prototyping",
            "Move into VS Code for structural control and deep development",
            "Use Claude Code to refine complex logic and logic flows",
            "Route AI requests through OpenRouter for model flexibility",
            "Test heavy lifting locally using Ollama to save on API limits",
            "Deploy instantly with Vercel for high-performance delivery"
          ].map((step, i) => (
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-brand-dark/30 rounded-xl border border-white/5">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brand-cyan/20 text-brand-cyan flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm">{i + 1}</span>
              <p class="text-brand-sky/90 m-0">{step}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>

        <!-- CTA Section -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-blue to-brand-dark p-12 rounded-[2rem] text-center relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_50%_50%,rgba(132,204,22,0.1),transparent_70%)]"></div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-6 relative z-10">Want an AI-Powered Website?</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-white/80 mb-10 relative z-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            We use this exact stack to build high-performance, conversion-focused sites faster than traditional agencies.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center relative z-10">
            <a href="/contact" class="cta-glow-shine bg-brand-accent text-[#0A0A0A] px-10 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-brand-accent-light">
              Start Your Project
            </a>
            <a href="tel:7044738188" class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md text-white border border-white/20 px-10 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-white/20 transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"/></svg>
              (704) 473-8188
            </a>
          </div>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-sm mt-8 relative z-10">
            Learn more about <a href="/about" class="text-white/60 hover:text-white underline underline-offset-4">Shelby Web Company</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer navigation -->
      <footer class="mt-24 pt-12 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-wrap gap-8 items-center justify-between">
        <a href="/blog" class="text-brand-sky/60 hover:text-white transition-colors flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
          Back to Blog
        </a>
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <a href="/" class="text-brand-sky/60 hover:text-white transition-colors">Home</a>
          <a href="/services/web-design" class="text-brand-sky/60 hover:text-white transition-colors">Web Design</a>
          <a href="/contact" class="text-brand-sky/60 hover:text-white transition-colors">Contact</a>
        </div>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
